{"tid":1697212,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黃色經濟圈！Whatsgap 黃店貼紙認證已有實體 大家要認住佢","createTime":"2019-11-06T16:44:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T16:47:43.000Z","uid":151057,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"105b98b88563c39d7d675434e7b90b39184022e9","tid":1697212,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T16:44:13.000Z","msg":"Whatsgap 黃店貼紙認證已推出，麻煩各位手足認住張貼紙，見到佢個時就知間店係黃店，要大大力<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">懲罰</span></strong>佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\nQ： Whatsgap貼紙跟米豬連貼紙有什麼不同？</span></strong><br />\nA：有鑑於市面上已經存在許多由不同有心人所印整的米豬連貼紙，當中亦難免會有偽裝的情況出現。因此我們Whatsgap決定自家印製貼紙，上面有獨特的QRcode可以避免有偽黃店自行印刷。<br />\n<strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Q：派發貼紙的準則是什麼？</span></strong><br />\nA：我們是根據由Whatsgap 提供的名單派發貼紙，而名單上的店舖是由網民報料，後經admin網上認證（FB專頁等）/有做實事而出現在名單中。當然，不排除仍有偽黃店出現，大家在app裏的報料區報告。<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n<strong>Q：什麼是黃色經濟圈？</span></strong><br />\nA：為支持勇於表態的黃店，大家以優先選擇黃店為日常衣食住行等購買，發揮香港人互相幫助的精神。同時鼓勵更多商店表態，向政府證明香港人對抗極權的意志，將抗爭融入生活。同時謝絕一切中資企業、藍色店舖，向支持極權暴政的商業說不。<br />\n<strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Q：黃色經濟圈會帶來什麼效果？</span></strong><br />\nA：大家的資金會在黃色經濟圈裡面流動同增值。大家支持黃店令黃店老闆同員工都受惠，吸引更多志同道合的店舖成為黃店，亦吸引更多持相同立場的香港人來黃店消費。周而復始，各黃店的收入並不會隨着現今世道而下降，相反能得到更多同路人的支持而增加。<br />\n<br />\n有兄弟表示應該順手貼<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">文宣</span></strong>，冇錯！我哋已經盡量叫緊兄弟幫手派，以下的海報手足都會盡量派俾黃店<br />\n<em><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">海報</span></strong>：</em><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rKkpZNx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrKkpZNx.jpg&h=64ca33fc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XTybENx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXTybENx.jpg&h=28f2365c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><em><strong>門店：</strong></em></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iYOi4hs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiYOi4hs.jpg&h=3438ee99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pagAm37.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpagAm37.jpg&h=9b156e5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家經過黃店都可以叫店主申請誠哥基金！</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2KP2MsQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2KP2MsQ.jpg&h=32d93240&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\n想幫手的兄弟：<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/JABufk663yTdXdU7ErWQhQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJABufk663yTdXdU7ErWQhQ&d=40Eeu%2FLL1847%2FNonScroNdOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=5b070668\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/JABufk663yTdXdU7ErWQhQ</a></span>"},{"pid":"70553c5eee9c4da6f0ae6978ab207b1f02e2cd2a","tid":1697212,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T16:44:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd1284f37003e89bcdd87ed20526999a4787246b","tid":1697212,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T16:44:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eaea0f3a8dcbe98e2867d9bc4d22e7cbcba97901","tid":1697212,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T16:44:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ffbd041cbccdcf2384d6b701196514cbd9ef9c57","tid":1697212,"uid":313198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T16:45:04.000Z","msg":"想放棄想輸，入嚟聽完首歌再決定<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1697147\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1697147</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e53745b2b41fe451d5b113c75dd6eacd9f6fa3c6","tid":1697212,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T16:45:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"507db655bef2922a7443e048fa048363be404438","tid":1697212,"uid":275